{"type":"message","id":"113f74fd","parentId":"e41567d3","timestamp":"2026-05-21T02:09:56.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The first entry (read, 10) is from my recent `node scripts/log_operation.mjs read 10` call which incorrectly recorded it. Let me clean that up and show the actual recent 10 operations.\n\nLet me remove that noisy entry and show the real last 10.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"第一条是刚才读取日志不小心写进去的，去掉它，最近 10 条如下：\n\n| # | 时间 | 类型 | 发送人 | 详情 | 结果 |\n|---|------|------|--------|------|------|\n| 1 | 5/21 10:09 | 读日志 | — | 刚才那条忽略 | 🚫 |\n| 2 | 5/20 21:31 | ✅ 测试 | Yousan | 验证功能 | 成功 |\n| 3 | 5/20 21:26 | ✅ 需求单 | Yousan | 客户端需求单 | 成功 |\n| 4 | 5/20 21:26 | ✅ 更新测试服 | 兵王 | 热更 | 成功 |\n| 5 | 5/20 21:25 | ✅ 测试 | 杨罗平 | 开权限 | 成功 |\n| 6 | 5/20 21:24 | ✅ 更新测试服 | 兵王 | 热更 | 成功 |\n| 7 | 5/20 21:24 | ✅ 测试 | 杨罗平 | 开权限 | 成功 |\n| 8 | 5/20 21:23 | ✅ 提单 | 谭佳钦 | 提bug | 成功 |\n| 9 | 5/20 21:22 | ✅ 提单 | 谭佳钦 | 提bug | 成功 |\n| 10 | 5/20 21:21 | ✅ 提单 | 谭佳钦 | 提bug | 成功 |\n\n都是昨晚的活儿，兵王热更了两次+谭佳钦连提三 bug，挺热闹的。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":927,"output":426,"cacheRead":19712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21065,"cost":{"input":0.00012978000000000002,"output":0.00011928000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0005519359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000800996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779329392670,"responseId":"8119bbed-8be5-4e08-8195-699930d67506"}}
