{"type":"message","id":"a284841d","parentId":"3a198032","timestamp":"2026-05-21T02:10:44.253Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说格式不错，是不是想让我把`read`功能加到`log_operation.mjs`脚本里，或者改进一下？让我先看看当前`log_operation.mjs`脚本，看下它的实现。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人喜欢这个表格格式？那我把它加到 `log_operation.mjs` 里，让 `read` 子命令输出这种格式的表。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_kzceRoVN5HTFLTB27s1f4824","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\log_operation.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3052,"output":140,"cacheRead":18048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21240,"cost":{"input":0.00042728000000000004,"output":0.000039200000000000004,"cacheRead":0.000505344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000971824}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779329441879,"responseId":"413457dd-4dac-4326-9517-f8a3310be63d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b74a7ce8","parentId":"a284841d","timestamp":"2026-05-21T02:10:44.348Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_kzceRoVN5HTFLTB27s1f4824","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 操作日志记录模块\n * 同事每次操作后调用，记录到 memory/operation-log.json\n * 自动发送飞书卡片到开发群。\n *\n * 用法: node scripts/log_operation.mjs <操作类型> <发送人> <详情> [结果]\n */\n\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst LOG_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'memory', 'operation-log.json');\n\nexport function logOperation({ type, sender, detail, result = '', senderId = '' }) {\n  const now = new Date();\n  const entry = {\n    timestamp: now.toISOString(),\n    time_cn: now.toLocaleString('zh-CN', { timeZone: 'Asia/Shanghai' }),\n    type, sender, senderId, detail, result,\n  };\n  let logs = [];\n  try { if (fs.existsSync(LOG_FILE)) logs = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(LOG_FILE, 'utf8')); } catch(e) {}\n  logs.push(entry);\n  if (logs.length > 500) logs = logs.slice(-500);\n  fs.writeFileSync(LOG_FILE, JSON.stringify(logs, null, 2), 'utf8');\n  return entry;\n}\n\n// CLI entry\nif (process.argv[1] === fileURLToPath(import.meta.url)) {\n  const type = process.argv[2];\n  const sender = process.argv[3];\n  const detail = process.argv[4] || '';\n  const result = process.argv[5] || '';\n  if (!type || !sender) { console.error('用法: node scripts/log_operation.mjs <操作类型> <发送人> <详情> [结果]'); process.exit(1); }\n  logOperation({ type, sender, detail, result });\n  console.log('✅ 已记录');\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779329444348}}
{"type":"message","id":"28634640","parentId":"b74a7ce8","timestamp":"2026-05-21T02:10:50.741Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll add a `read` subcommand that prints the last N entries in a nice table format. The current code uses `process.argv[1] === fileURLToPath(import.meta.url)` to detect CLI mode, but the `read` command was previously handled wrong (just stored as a log entry). Let me fix the CLI to support `read` as a subcommand properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_RClusIFEiV5Sy7MTRfn89896","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\log_operation.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"// CLI entry\nif (process.argv[1] === fileURLToPath(import.meta.url)) {\n  const type = process.argv[2];\n  const sender = process.argv[3];\n  const detail = process.argv[4] || '';\n  const result = process.argv[5] || '';\n  if (!type || !sender) { console.error('用法: node scripts/log_operation.mjs <操作类型> <发送人> <详情> [结果]'); process.exit(1); }\n  logOperation({ type, sender, detail, result });\n  console.log('✅ 已记录');\n}","newText":"function readLogs(count = 10) {\n  let logs = [];\n  try {\n    if (fs.existsSync(LOG_FILE)) logs = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(LOG_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  } catch(e) {}\n  const recent = logs.slice(-count).reverse();\n  if (recent.length === 0) { console.log('暂无日志'); return; }\n  // Pretty table\n  const header = `| # | 时间 | 类型 | 发送人 | 详情 | 结果 |`;\n  const separator = `|---|------|------|--------|------|------|`;\n  const rows = recent.map((e, i) => {\n    const n = recent.length - i;\n    const type = e.type && e.type.length > 8 ? e.type.slice(0, 6) + '…' : (e.type || '');\n    const detail = e.detail && e.detail.length > 10 ? e.detail.slice(0, 9) + '…' : (e.detail || '');\n    const result = e.result || '';\n    const icon = result === '成功' ? '✅' : result === '失败' ? '❌' : '—';\n    return `| ${n} | ${e.time_cn || '—'} | ${icon} ${type} | ${e.sender || '—'} | ${detail} | ${result || '—'} |`;\n  }).join('\\n');\n  console.log(`\\n📋 最近 ${recent.length} 条操作日志:\\n`);\n  console.log(header);\n  console.log(separator);\n  console.log(rows);\n  console.log();\n}\n\n// CLI entry\nif (process.argv[1] === fileURLToPath(import.meta.url)) {\n  const subcmd = process.argv[2];\n  if (subcmd === 'read') {\n    const n = parseInt(process.argv[3], 10) || 10;\n    readLogs(n);\n    process.exit(0);\n  }\n  const type = subcmd;\n  const sender = process.argv[3];\n  const detail = process.argv[4] || '';\n  const result = process.argv[5] || '';\n  if (!type || !sender) { console.error('用法:\\n  node scripts/log_operation.mjs <操作类型> <发送人> <详情> [结果]  记录日志\\n  node scripts/log_operation.mjs read [条数]                     查看日志'); process.exit(1); }\n  logOperation({ type, sender, detail, result });\n  console.log('✅ 已记录');\n}","oldTextMatchMode":"exact"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":560,"output":952,"cacheRead":21120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22632,"cost":{"input":0.00007840000000000001,"output":0.00026656,"cacheRead":0.00059136,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00093632}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779329444349,"responseId":"d8faf982-dba8-4b9f-bcb1-d29e13503cdb"}}
