{"type":"message","id":"06d0ba1d","parentId":"838f3fbd","timestamp":"2026-05-21T03:53:32.085Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"胡新雷的GitLab用户ID是1836，用户名@v-huxinlei。现在我需要在某个项目上把他改成Reporter来测试。让我先看看他在哪些项目中有权限 - 比如看看核心仓库里的情况。\n\n不过主人没说具体哪个项目。让我先看看核心仓库里胡新雷的成员状态，找个他已经在的项目来测试 update 功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了，胡新雷 `@v-huxinlei` id=1836。先看看他在核心仓库里的情况："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_bYwlJrKaT9Q1uJ9hoeJD5249","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node scripts/git_permission.mjs list 5058","workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_R3OcaH0BrDk1zYfa0CWC7892","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node scripts/git_permission.mjs list 4710","workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":108,"output":260,"cacheRead":34176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34544,"cost":{"input":0.000015120000000000001,"output":0.00007280000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000956928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0010448480000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779335609439,"responseId":"aadc31e1-c9c3-407e-8e76-70385ba0a39c"}}
