{"type":"message","id":"3995495a","parentId":"64974309","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:01:59.489Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the login page clearly:\n\n1. **LDAP** form: `https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/users/auth/ldapmain/callback` - uses company domain account\n2. **Standard** form: `https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/users/sign_in` - standard GitLab login\n3. **SSO**: `https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/users/auth/openid_connect` - OIDC SSO\n\nThe LDAP login uses company domain accounts (the prompt says \"请点击LDAP,并使用域账户登录\"). So the user needs to use their company LDAP credentials to log in.\n\nThis means I need to open a headed browser and let the user enter their LDAP credentials manually. The login form has:\n- authenticity_token (CSRF token)\n- username (LDAP username)\n- password (LDAP password)\n\nLet me reopen a headed browser properly this time. The previous browser was closed, so let me start fresh.\n\nActually, since opening additional browser windows was confusing, let me just clean up the temp files first, then explain to the user what happened and what I need.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5yYYGNs5AxR60r6IIOP40671","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for %f in (scripts\\_gitlab_*.mjs) do del \"%f\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":583,"output":331,"cacheRead":50688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51602,"cost":{"input":0.00008162000000000001,"output":0.00009268,"cacheRead":0.001419264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001593564}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779336115719,"responseId":"c039b034-1b38-48c4-ae95-edf9660c3ab4"}}
