{"type":"message","id":"1ea1bc2a","parentId":"61944cff","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:02:04.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, cleanup done. Now let me explain the situation to the user.\n\nThe issue is:\n1. GitLab uses LDAP login (company domain account) - not a simple web cookies situation\n2. I need the user to manually log in through a browser\n3. After login, I can get both the session cookie and CSRF token for API calls\n\nLet me tell the user what's happening and what I need, then offer to open the browser.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，GitLab 用的是公司 LDAP 域账户登录，不是第三方扫码。刚才我开浏览器登录没成功——因为登录页需要手动输账号密码（域账户）。\n\n我需要开个浏览器窗口让主人登录一下 GitLab，登录成功后我就能拿到 Cookie + CSRF Token，这样写操作（添加/修改成员）才能正常用。\n\n要不我再开一次浏览器？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":117,"output":175,"cacheRead":51712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52004,"cost":{"input":0.000016380000000000002,"output":0.000049000000000000005,"cacheRead":0.001447936,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001513316}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779336121833,"responseId":"fcab50dc-5f4c-4cdc-8f20-2f1b3ee1d309"}}
