{"type":"message","id":"5fff937a","parentId":"cb497a39","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:03:19.415Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is:\n1. The CSRF token was not found (⚠️ 未找到) - it shows 「请主人登录 GitLab...」 then 「CSRF Token: ⚠️ 未找到」 without logging success. This means the waitForURL failed or the login was detected but the page didn't have a CSRF token.\n\nActually wait, looking more carefully: \n- \"当前页面: https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/users/sign_in\"\n- \"请主人登录 GitLab...\"\n- Then immediately \"CSRF Token: ⚠️ 未找到\"\n\nThis means `waitForURL` didn't actually wait - it didn't detect the URL change. The `waitForURL` with a function argument in Playwright might not have worked properly.\n\nAlso the path issue: `C:\\C:\\Users...` - double C: prefix. The `new URL()` is resolving incorrectly. Let me fix both issues.\n\nLet me rewrite with:\n1. Simple path instead of URL()\n2. Better wait logic","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"路径有双 `C:` 问题，我来修一下。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_zFqA6dtCIiew1289uU3w0517","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\n\nconst COOKIE_FILE = 'C:/Users/yyzypublic/.openclaw/workspace/gitlab_cookies.json';\nconst CSRF_FILE = 'C:/Users/yyzypublic/.openclaw/workspace/gitlab_csrf.json';\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\nconst context = await browser.newContext();\nconst page = await context.newPage();\n\nconsole.log('正在打开 GitLab...');\nawait page.goto('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/', { waitUntil: 'networkidle' });\nconsole.log('当前页面:', page.url());\nconsole.log('请主人登录 GitLab（LDAP 域账户）。登录成功后自动继续...');\n\n// Wait for login - check URL every 2 seconds\nlet loggedIn = false;\nfor (let i = 0; i < 300; i++) {\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n  const url = page.url();\n  if (!url.includes('sign_in')) {\n    loggedIn = true;\n    console.log('登录成功! 当前页面:', url);\n    break;\n  }\n}\n\nif (!loggedIn) {\n  console.log('登录超时');\n  await browser.close();\n  process.exit(1);\n}\n\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n// Get CSRF token from page\nconst csrfToken = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const meta = document.querySelector('meta[name=\"csrf-token\"]');\n  return meta ? meta.getAttribute('content') : null;\n});\n\n// Save cookies\nconst cookies = await context.cookies();\nfs.writeFileSync(COOKIE_FILE, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\nconsole.log(`Cookies 已保存: ${cookies.length} 个`);\n\n// Save CSRF token\nif (csrfToken) {\n  fs.writeFileSync(CSRF_FILE, JSON.stringify({ csrfToken, timestamp: new Date().toISOString() }, null, 2));\n  console.log('CSRF Token 已保存 ✓');\n} else {\n  console.log('CSRF Token: ⚠️ 未找到');\n}\n\nconst gs = cookies.find(c => c.name === '_gitlab_session');\nconsole.log('Session:', gs ? '有效 ✓' : '⚠️ 无效');\n\nconsole.log('\\n✅ 登录完成!');\nawait browser.close();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\_gitlab_login.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":441,"output":821,"cacheRead":52736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53998,"cost":{"input":0.00006174,"output":0.00022988000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001476608,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001768228}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779336193448,"responseId":"48177902-1d52-45f1-b0d5-ccdaf286a875"}}
