{"type":"message","id":"147cf829","parentId":"1a48e80c","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:03:45.113Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still 401. The OIDC login flow wasn't completed - the user is still on Keycloak's login page. Let me re-run the login script but this time wait for the user to complete BOTH the GitLab sign-in AND the Keycloak SSO, so we end up on a proper GitLab project page.\n\nLet me update the script to:\n1. First wait for URL to leave `sign_in` (user clicks LDAP or SSO)\n2. Then wait for URL to contain `git.devcloud.ztgame.com` again (SSO callback complete, back on GitLab)\n3. Or just wait until the page URL contains the GitLab dashboard/home page","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"SSO 流程没走完——还要在 Keycloak 页面上输密码。我再开一次，这次一直等到真正回到 GitLab 页面。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_dUuI4kHnEGtGhGmU8mRr9997","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\n\nconst COOKIE_FILE = 'C:/Users/yyzypublic/.openclaw/workspace/gitlab_cookies.json';\nconst CSRF_FILE = 'C:/Users/yyzypublic/.openclaw/workspace/gitlab_csrf.json';\n\nconst browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: false });\nconst context = await browser.newContext();\nconst page = await context.newPage();\n\nconsole.log('打开 GitLab...');\nawait page.goto('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/', { waitUntil: 'networkidle' });\nconsole.log('当前:', page.url());\nconsole.log('请主人登录。注意：GitLab 会先跳到 Keycloak SSO 页面，需要再登录一次。');\nconsole.log('我会一直等到回到 GitLab 页面。');\n\n// Keep checking until we're back on git.devcloud.ztgame.com (not sign_in, not keycloak)\nlet loggedIn = false;\nfor (let i = 0; i < 300; i++) {\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 2000));\n  const url = page.url();\n  if (url.startsWith('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/') && !url.includes('sign_in') && !url.includes('auth')) {\n    loggedIn = true;\n    console.log('\\n✅ 登录完成! URL:', url);\n    break;\n  }\n}\n\nif (!loggedIn) {\n  console.log('登录超时');\n  await browser.close();\n  process.exit(1);\n}\n\nawait page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n// Get CSRF token\nconst csrfToken = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const meta = document.querySelector('meta[name=\"csrf-token\"]');\n  return meta ? meta.getAttribute('content') : null;\n});\n\n// Save cookies\nconst cookies = await context.cookies();\nfs.writeFileSync(COOKIE_FILE, JSON.stringify(cookies, null, 2));\nconsole.log(`Cookies: ${cookies.length} 个`);\n\n// Save CSRF\nif (csrfToken) {\n  fs.writeFileSync(CSRF_FILE, JSON.stringify({ csrfToken, timestamp: new Date().toISOString() }, null, 2));\n  console.log('CSRF Token: ✓');\n} else {\n  console.log('CSRF Token: ⚠️ 未找到');\n}\n\nconst gs = cookies.find(c => c.name === '_gitlab_session');\nconsole.log('Session:', gs ? '✓' : '⚠️ 无效');\n\nawait browser.close();\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\_gitlab_login.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":34,"output":807,"cacheRead":55296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56137,"cost":{"input":0.00000476,"output":0.00022596,"cacheRead":0.0015482879999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017790079999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779336219357,"responseId":"8c4ecda5-2ddc-4cc6-b53f-e94e7c4ec651"}}
