{"type":"message","id":"e512c50c","parentId":"f8b0d908","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:04:57.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update the API usage section to include CSRF token note.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_HsaWXSqdjeSDkFQvrTzB9055","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/gitlab-permission/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"```javascript\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n```","newText":"## 认证方式\n\nGitLab 使用公司 Keycloak SSO 登录（LDAP/CAS），需要从已登录的浏览器获取 Cookie + CSRF Token。\n\n**Cookie 文件:** `workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`\n**CSRF Token 文件:** `workspace/gitlab_csrf.json`\n\n**写操作（POST/PUT/DELETE）** 需要 `X-CSRF-Token` 头，否则返回 401。\n登录方式：打开 headed 浏览器 → 手动 SSO 登录（先点 SSO → Keycloak 再输一次密码）→ 自动保存 Cookie + CSRF Token。\n\n```javascript\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\nconst writeHeaders = { ...headers, 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded', 'X-CSRF-Token': csrfToken };\nconst GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n```\n\n> `git_permission.mjs` 已自动处理 CSRF Token：`getHeaders()` 用于读取，`getWriteHeaders()` 用于写入。"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":133,"output":454,"cacheRead":65152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65739,"cost":{"input":0.00001862,"output":0.00012712000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001824256,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001969996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779336293872,"responseId":"94d5bc58-c8f6-4f5b-b564-8cb1dab3a17d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d37a68b9","parentId":"e512c50c","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:04:57.821Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_HsaWXSqdjeSDkFQvrTzB9055","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in ~/.openclaw/plugin-skills/gitlab-permission/SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  54 | 胡新雷 | @v-huxinlei | 1836 |\n  55 \n  56 ## API 用法\n  57 \n+ 58 ## 认证方式\n+ 59 \n+ 60 GitLab 使用公司 Keycloak SSO 登录（LDAP/CAS），需要从已登录的浏览器获取 Cookie + CSRF Token。\n+ 61 \n+ 62 **Cookie 文件:** `workspace/gitlab_cookies.json`\n+ 63 **CSRF Token 文件:** `workspace/gitlab_csrf.json`\n+ 64 \n+ 65 **写操作（POST/PUT/DELETE）** 需要 `X-CSRF-Token` 头，否则返回 401。\n+ 66 登录方式：打开 headed 浏览器 → 手动 SSO 登录（先点 SSO → Keycloak 再输一次密码）→ 自动保存 Cookie + CSRF Token。\n+ 67 \n  58 ```javascript\n  59 const cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\n  60 const headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\n+ 71 const writeHeaders = { ...headers, 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded', 'X-CSRF-Token': csrfToken };\n  61 const GITLAB = 'https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com';\n  62 ```\n  63 \n+ 75 > `git_permission.mjs` 已自动处理 CSRF Token：`getHeaders()` 用于读取，`getWriteHeaders()` 用于写入。\n+ 76 \n  64 ### 查询项目成员\n  65 ```bash\n  66 GET /api/v4/projects/{project_id}/members/all?per_page=100\n  67 ```\n     ...","firstChangedLine":58},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779336297821}}
