{"type":"message","id":"fca74099","parentId":"06641623","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:05:36.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `known_sign_in` cookie expires on June 4, 2026 — about 14 days from now. Good, this is a persistent session.\n\nNow I need to check if the CSRF token from before is still valid. The CSRF token is page-specific - it changes periodically. Let me try to get a fresh CSRF token by fetching a GitLab page.\n\nOr let me just test the write operation and see what happens.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_dFyRHa3NRhUsckt0DtOq7560","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node scripts/git_permission.mjs update 2751 胡新雷 reporter 2>&1","workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":147,"output":184,"cacheRead":70272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70603,"cost":{"input":0.000020580000000000003,"output":0.00005152,"cacheRead":0.001967616,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002039716}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779336334425,"responseId":"1e652b37-e380-4d03-86a9-dbd09f6ebbff"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d31ab58","parentId":"fca74099","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:05:36.969Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_dFyRHa3NRhUsckt0DtOq7560","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"node : 鉂?澶辫触: 401 Unauthorized\r\n所在位置 行:1 字符: 1\r\n+ node scripts/git_permission.mjs update 2751 胡新雷 reporter 2>&1\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (鉂?澶辫触: 401 Unauthorized:String) [], RemoteException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : NativeCommandError\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":404,"aggregated":"node : 鉂?澶辫触: 401 Unauthorized\r\n所在位置 行:1 字符: 1\r\n+ node scripts/git_permission.mjs update 2751 胡新雷 reporter 2>&1\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : NotSpecified: (鉂?澶辫触: 401 Unauthorized:String) [], RemoteException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : NativeCommandError\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779336336968}}
{"type":"message","id":"153f79a2","parentId":"5d31ab58","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:05:40.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The write goes to 401 again - CSRF token is stale. I need to get a fresh CSRF token from a GitLab page using these cookies. Let me write a quick script to do that.\n\nActually, let me think about this more carefully. The CSRF token is embedded in `<meta name=\"csrf-token\">` in GitLab's HTML pages. I need to:\n1. Fetch any GitLab page (like the dashboard) with the cookie\n2. Extract the CSRF token from the HTML meta tag\n\nThis is a simple fetch operation - no need for Playwright.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"CSRF Token 过期了，写操作又 401 了。需要拿 Cookie 去 GitLab 页面抓个新的 CSRF Token："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Te8sw1B6Fx2dhghtSQdr6372","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import fs from 'fs';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('gitlab_cookies.json', 'utf8'));\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'text/html' };\n\n// Fetch GitLab dashboard to extract CSRF token\nconst r = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/', { headers });\nconst html = await r.text();\n\n// Extract CSRF token from meta tag\nconst match = html.match(/<meta name=\"csrf-token\" content=\"([^\"]+)\"\\s*\\/?>/i);\nif (match) {\n  const csrfToken = match[1];\n  fs.writeFileSync('gitlab_csrf.json', JSON.stringify({ csrfToken, timestamp: new Date().toISOString() }, null, 2));\n  console.log('✅ 新 CSRF Token 已获取');\n  console.log('Token 前20位:', csrfToken.substring(0, 20) + '...');\n} else {\n  console.log('❌ 未找到 CSRF Token');\n  // Debug: show first 2000 chars of HTML\n  console.log('HTML 前500字:', html.substring(0, 500));\n}\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\_refresh_csrf.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":202,"output":509,"cacheRead":70528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71239,"cost":{"input":0.00002828,"output":0.00014252,"cacheRead":0.001974784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002145584}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779336336970,"responseId":"84cb7a0e-3029-4d98-aeb1-772c4917ce39"}}
