{"type":"message","id":"9542393d","parentId":"1a746883","timestamp":"2026-05-21T06:26:20.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人说 gameconfig(4710) 项目里胡新雷还是 Developer。让我查一下这个项目里他的实际权限。可能的原因是：\n\n1. 胡新雷可能是通过组继承来的 Developer 权限（组的权限 > 直接成员的权限）\n2. GitLab 的权限继承规则：如果用户属于某个组，组的权限会覆盖直接成员权限\n\n在 GitLab 中，用户可以通过两种方式成为项目成员：\n1. 直接添加为项目成员（我们操作的就是这种）\n2. 属于某个组，组有项目的权限（组的权限会覆盖个人的权限）\n\n如果某个组（比如 Developer 组）已经包含了胡新雷且组权限是 Developer，那不管我们怎么设置他的个人权限为 Reporter，他的实际权限还是 Developer（因为组权限更高）。\n\n让我们通过 API 检查一下，看看他的实际 access_level 和是不是来自组继承。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_JAAZdhuB5IVpkdhgXEHB0171","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import fs from 'fs';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('gitlab_cookies.json', 'utf8'));\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\n\n// Check user 1836 in project 4710\nconst r = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/projects/4710/members/1836', { headers });\nconst d = await r.json();\nconsole.log('GET /members/1836:');\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(d, null, 2));\n\n// Also check members/all which includes inherited members\nconst r2 = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/projects/4710/members/all?search=胡新雷', { headers });\nconst d2 = await r2.json();\nconsole.log('\\nGET /members/all?search=胡新雷:');\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify(d2, null, 2));\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\_check_member.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1210,"output":490,"cacheRead":79488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81188,"cost":{"input":0.00016940000000000002,"output":0.0001372,"cacheRead":0.002225664,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002532264}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779344772277,"responseId":"0c626991-0ce3-4321-938b-bc9e962af028"}}
