{"type":"message","id":"7df04b6d","parentId":"03c9eb02","timestamp":"2026-05-21T06:26:32.174Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"From the first API call `GET /projects/4710/members/1836`, it returns only direct members (not inherited). It shows:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 1836,\n  \"username\": \"v-huxinlei\",\n  \"name\": \"胡新雷\",\n  \"access_level\": 20,\n  ...\n  \"created_by\": { \"id\": 983, \"username\": \"yezhijun\", \"name\": \"叶枝君\" }\n}\n```\n\nSo:\n1. The direct member permission IS `access_level: 20` (Reporter) ✅ - Our API change worked!\n2. It was created by 叶枝君 (me) ✅\n\nBut the owner says on the web UI it still shows Developer. This means胡新雷 also belongs to a group (like a Developer group) that has access to this project. In GitLab, if a user is in a group with Developer access and also a direct member with Reporter access, the higher permission (Developer from the group) wins.\n\nThe `GET /members/1836` returns only direct membership, while `GET /members/all` would include inherited members. But `/members/all` with `search` parameter doesn't return his info because... actually looking at the output, the search returned many users but NOT 胡新雷. That's because `search` on `members/all` filters by name/username and the pagination might have cut him off.\n\nLet me check more specifically for his membership in the project, including inherited group membership.\n\nActually, let me use the `GET /projects/4710/members/all?page=1&per_page=100` to check all members including inherited. But the list had 100 members before. Let me search specifically for 胡新雷.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CjUtv9GvwyCt4tLbIwrA6672","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import fs from 'fs';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('gitlab_cookies.json', 'utf8'));\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\n\n// Check all members including inherited, search by name\nconst r = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/projects/4710/members/all?per_page=200', { headers });\nconst members = await r.json();\nconst hx = members.find(m => m.id === 1836);\nif (hx) {\n  console.log('胡新雷在 members/all 中的信息:');\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(hx, null, 2));\n} else {\n  console.log('❌ 在 members/all 中未找到胡新雷');\n}\n\n// Check if there's a source field (group membership)\nconsole.log('\\n--- 检查所有权源 ---');\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\_check_member2.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4435,"output":667,"cacheRead":81280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86382,"cost":{"input":0.0006209000000000001,"output":0.00018676,"cacheRead":0.00227584,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0030835}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779344783090,"responseId":"0d1f5507-b733-4417-944c-b56163248d57"}}
