{"type":"message","id":"0bd5fe0f","parentId":"7b2549ab","timestamp":"2026-05-21T06:27:14.986Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So project 4710 (gameconfig) belongs to these groups:\n1. `yyzy_proj/gordian` (id=5981)\n2. `yyzy_proj` (id=1222) - the parent group\n\nNow if 胡新雷 is a member of either of these groups with Developer access, that would explain why his effective permission is Developer.\n\nThe `access_level: undefined` in the response is because the groups API returns the share level, not the group's actual access_level for this project.\n\nLet me check the members of the `yyzy_proj/gordian` group to see if 胡新雷 is in it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GE2ixyGkdQhg1x74jwS61023","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import fs from 'fs';\n\nconst cookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('gitlab_cookies.json', 'utf8'));\nconst cookieStr = cookies.map(c => `${c.name}=${c.value}`).join('; ');\nconst headers = { 'Cookie': cookieStr, 'Accept': 'application/json' };\n\n// Check group 5981 members for 胡新雷\nconst r = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/groups/5981/members/all?per_page=100&page=1', { headers });\nconst members = await r.json();\nconst hx = Array.isArray(members) ? members.find(m => m.id === 1836) : null;\nif (hx) {\n  console.log('胡新雷在组 yyzy_proj/gordian 中:');\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(hx, null, 2));\n} else {\n  console.log('胡新雷不在 yyzy_proj/gordian 组中');\n}\n\n// Check parent group 1222\nconst r2 = await fetch('https://git.devcloud.ztgame.com/api/v4/groups/1222/members/all?per_page=200&page=1', { headers });\nconst members2 = await r2.json();\nconst hx2 = Array.isArray(members2) ? members2.find(m => m.id === 1836) : null;\nif (hx2) {\n  console.log('\\n胡新雷在父组 yyzy_proj 中:');\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(hx2, null, 2));\n} else {\n  console.log('\\n胡新雷不在父组 yyzy_proj 中');\n}\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\_check_groups.mj