{"type":"message","id":"820983fb","parentId":"8bd54739","timestamp":"2026-05-21T06:27:44.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No `source` field in either response. The `members/all` API returns a flat list of members without distinguishing direct vs inherited in the response.\n\nBut the data shows: `access_level: 30` for `members/all`, while direct `members/1836` returned `access_level: 20`.\n\nThis is the key GitLab behavior: when a user is both a direct member AND in a group, the effective permission is the maximum of the two. Since the direct member was set to Reporter(20) but the effective is Developer(30), there must be a group somewhere giving him Developer access.\n\nSince he's not in `yyzy_proj/gordian` or `yyzy_proj` directly, maybe he's in a subgroup of `yyzy_proj` that inherits access to this project.\n\nHowever, I don't have admin access to check all group memberships. Let me think about what to tell the owner.\n\nThe situation is:\n- API direct member query → 20 (Reporter) ✅ Our change worked\n- API effective (members/all) → 30 (Developer) ❌ Group override\n- Web UI shows → 30 (Developer) because the UI shows effective permission\n\nSo the issue is that 胡新雷 belongs to a group that has Developer access to the gameconfig project. We need to either:\n1. Figure out which group and remove him from it\n2. Or lower the group's access level for this project\n\nLet me present this to the owner.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_M8cRwu3g9om0CzjMtMEG9732","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"del scripts\\_check_member.mjs scripts\\_check_member2.mjs scripts\\_check_member3.mjs scripts\\_check_groups.mjs","workdir":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":409,"output":414,"cacheRead":99840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100663,"cost":{"input":0.000057260000000000004,"output":0.00011592,"cacheRead":0.00279552,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029687000000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779344858124,"responseId":"985ad807-5dd5-4b3e-8a12-06d1d84031ef"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e503b30e","parentId":"820983fb","timestamp":"2026-05-21T06:27:44.551Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_M8cRwu3g9om0CzjMtMEG9732","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Remove-Item : 找不到接受实际参数“scripts\\_check_member2.mjs”的位置形式参数。\r\n所在位置 行:1 字符: 1\r\n+ del scripts\\_check_member.mjs scripts\\_check_member2.mjs scripts\\_che ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidArgument: (:) [Remove-Item]，ParameterBindingException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : PositionalParameterNotFound,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.RemoveItemCommand\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":291,"aggregated":"Remove-Item : 找不到接受实际参数“scripts\\_check_member2.mjs”的位置形式参数。\r\n所在位置 行:1 字符: 1\r\n+ del scripts\\_check_member.mjs scripts\\_check_member2.mjs scripts\\_che ...\r\n+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidArgument: (:) [Remove-Item]，ParameterBindingException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : PositionalParameterNotFound,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.RemoveItemCommand\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779344864551}}
