{"type":"message","id":"dcab0460","parentId":"4850f5ce","timestamp":"2026-05-21T06:27:56.294Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, temp files cleaned. Now let me explain the situation to the owner.\n\nThe root cause:\n- Our API set 胡新雷's direct permission to Reporter(20) ✅\n- But his effective permission is Developer(30) due to group membership\n- GitLab uses `max(direct_level, group_level)` for the effective permission\n\nI don't have admin access to list user's group memberships (403 on /users/:id/memberships), so I can't pinpoint exactly which group gives him Developer. The owner might know or can check on the web UI.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，问题查到了！\n\n**直接成员权限已成功改为 Reporter(20)** ✅ API 确认无误。\n\n但 gameconfig 项目上胡新雷的**有效权限**是 **Developer(30)**，说明他属于某个有 Developer 权限的组（组权限覆盖个人设置）。GitLab 的规则是取个人和组中的最高权限，所以 30 > 20，页面显示 Developer。\n\n补充 5 个仓库的实际状态：\n\n| 仓库 | 直接权限 | 有效权限 | 说明 |\n|------|---------|---------|------|\n| config(5058) | Reporter ✅ | 待查 | — |\n| gameconfig(4710) | Reporter ✅ | **Developer** ⚠️ | 被组权限覆盖 |\n| DidaFramework(5048) | Reporter ✅ | 待查 | — |\n| battle1v1(5145) | Reporter ✅ | 待查 | — |\n| proto(5060) | Reporter ✅ | 待查 | — |\n\n想看下其他 4 个仓库的有效权限吗？或者你知道胡新雷在哪个组里（比如研发组、项目组之类的），我可以看看能不能把他从组里移除。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":150,"output":372,"cacheRead":100992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101514,"cost":{"input":0.000021000000000000002,"output":0.00010416,"cacheRead":0.0028277759999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029529359999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779344868632,"responseId":"e5d65f40-8a47-46c3-a9dd-bdc2b0ad5d7c"}}
