{"type":"message","id":"76ba7c03","parentId":"39c15409","timestamp":"2026-05-21T07:16:46.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me just add a note to AGENTS.md about checking the skills manifest.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_RIe4rVoYoM3EM5mO49TT9544","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\AGENTS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"## Tools\n\nSkills provide your tools. When you need one, check its `SKILL.md`. Keep local notes (camera names, SSH details, voice preferences) in `TOOLS.md`.","newText":"## Skills & Versioning\n\nSkills provide your tools. When you need one, check its `SKILL.md`.\n\n**技能版本同步：** 每次使用技能前，先读 `memory/skills-manifest.json` 检查版本号。\n如果清单里的版本比你记忆中的新，说明技能已更新，重新读 SKILL.md 取最新内容。\n这个清单由修改技能的人负责更新。\n\nKeep local notes (camera names, SSH details, voice preferences) in `TOOLS.md`."}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":461,"output":260,"cacheRead":113280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114001,"cost":{"input":0.00006454,"output":0.00007280000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00317184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00330918}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779347801578,"responseId":"fdeb6190-9f8d-4b34-847b-22d13ea37b79"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1d385835","parentId":"76ba7c03","timestamp":"2026-05-21T07:16:46.244Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_RIe4rVoYoM3EM5mO49TT9544","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\AGENTS.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 133 Reactions are lightweight social signals. Humans use them constantly — they say \"I saw this, I acknowledge you\" without cluttering the chat. You should too.\n 134 \n 135 **Don't overdo it:** One reaction per message max. Pick the one that fits best.\n 136 \n-137 ## Tools\n+137 ## Skills & Versioning\n 138 \n-139 Skills provide your tools. When you need one, check its `SKILL.md`. Keep local notes (camera names, SSH details, voice preferences) in `TOOLS.md`.\n+139 Skills provide your tools. When you need one, check its `SKILL.md`.\n 140 \n+141 **技能版本同步：** 每次使用技能前，先读 `memory/skills-manifest.json` 检查版本号。\n+142 如果清单里的版本比你记忆中的新，说明技能已更新，重新读 SKILL.md 取最新内容。\n+143 这个清单由修改技能的人负责更新。\n+144 \n+145 Keep local notes (camera names, SSH details, voice preferences) in `TOOLS.md`.\n+146 \n 141 **🎭 Voice Storytelling:** If you have `sag` (ElevenLabs TTS), use voice for stories, movie summaries, and \"storytime\" moments! Way more engaging than walls of text. Surprise people with funny voices.\n 142 \n 143 **📝 Platform Formatting:**\n 144 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":137},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779347806244}}
{"type":"message","id":"f920edfe","parentId":"1d385835","timestamp":"2026-05-21T07:16:50.709Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me summarize what I've set up for the owner.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了！以后更新技能的流程是这样的：\n\n**自动同步机制：**\n\n```\n更新技能文件（SKILL.md / 脚本）\n  ↓\nBump memory/skills-manifest.json 中的版本号\n  ↓\n新任务到来时 → 查 manifest → 比对版本 → 发现新版 → 重新读 SKILL.md\n```\n\n**已部署：**\n- ✅ `memory/skills-manifest.json` — 技能版本清单\n- ✅ `AGENTS.md` — 已加入\"每次用技能先查版本\"的规则\n- ✅ `MEMORY.md` — 已记录版本管理方案\n- ✅ `HEARTBEAT.md` — 保活不受影响\n\n现在不管哪个 session，只要用到技能，都会先检查版本号。如果有更新就自动重读，不会再用旧版了 🌸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":121,"output":192,"cacheRead":113920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114233,"cost":{"input":0.00001694,"output":0.00005376,"cacheRead":0.00318976,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032604599999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779347806247,"responseId":"933e6b51-b530-47d9-85fe-38837944cf1a"}}
